rows.label: xs33670100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Well! This is a discovery that will turn
galactic history on its head![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33670100_MSG0020
rows.name: And here is where we made it...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33670100_MSG0030
rows.name:
To think I'd get to stand amidst
genuine Samaarian ruins...![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33670100_MSG0040
rows.name:
And then, this inexplicable space...
Could it be part of the "rift between worlds"?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33670100_MSG0050
rows.name:
Oh my heart, the sheer wonder of it!
I have to take in all I can![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33670100_MSG0060
rows.name: Quickly! This is a golden opportunity![ST:wait ]
